---
import Layout from "../../../layouts/MonkedLayout.astro";

const lastUpdated = "January 27, 2026";
const contactEmail = "hello@asantinos.com";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy - Monked"
  description="Privacy Policy for Monked app"
>
  <main class="min-h-screen px-6 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <a
        href="/"
        class="text-sm text-neutral-500 hover:text-neutral-300 transition-colors"
      >
        &larr; Back to Monked
      </a>

      <h1 class="mt-8 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>

      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-neutral-500">
        Last updated: {lastUpdated}
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8 space-y-8 text-neutral-400">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-100">Overview</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Monked is designed to be calm, private, and distraction-free. We do
            not collect, sell, or share your personal data. All information is
            stored locally on your device.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-100">
            What data Monked accesses
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Monked does not access system data such as contacts, location, or
            health information. All data used by the app is created directly by
            you.
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-3 list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
            <li>Habit data: habit names, goals, and completion logs.</li>
            <li>Journal entries: text you write inside the app.</li>
            <li>Meditation sessions: duration and timestamps.</li>
            <li>Storage: on-device only.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-100">
            What data we collect
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Monked does not collect any personal data. In particular:
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-3 list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
            <li>No accounts or sign-in.</li>
            <li>No analytics or tracking identifiers.</li>
            <li>No advertising SDKs.</li>
            <li>No location data.</li>
            <li>No data is sent to external servers.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-100">Data sharing</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Monked does not transmit your data to external servers and does not
            share information with third parties. Everything remains on your
            device.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-100">
            Third-party services
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Monked does not integrate with third-party analytics, advertising,
            or tracking services.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-100">
            Your choices and controls
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-2">You are fully in control of your data:</p>
          <ul class="mt-3 list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
            <li>All data can be deleted at any time by removing the app.</li>
            <li>
              Monked does not store data on servers, so there is nothing to
              request, export, or delete outside your device.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-100">
            Children’s privacy
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Monked does not knowingly collect personal information from anyone,
            including children. The app has no accounts, no social features, and
            no data collection.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-100">
            Changes to this policy
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            If Monked’s privacy practices change, this policy will be updated
            and the “Last updated” date will be revised.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-100">Contact</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, you can contact
            me at{" "}
            <a
              href={`mailto:${contactEmail}`}
              class="text-neutral-200 underline decoration-neutral-700 underline-offset-4 hover:text-neutral-100 hover:decoration-neutral-500 transition-colors"
            >
              {contactEmail}
            </a>
            .
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
